<description>* Based on The Adventures of Tom Sawyer by http://anidb.net/cr6174 [Mark Twain].
Tom is a rustic, wild and mischievous boy living with his younger brother Sid, his aunt Polly, and Polly`s daughter Mary. Following the death of their parents, Polly has raised her sister`s two kids as though they were her own children, with love and affection. Tom spends most of his time with his best friend http://anidb.net/ch28989 [Huckleberry Finn] sharing all sorts of thrilling activities and adventures such as chasing wild pigs, playing pirates in the Mississippi River, and riding a balloon. While enjoying various adventures and excitement, Tom and Huck happen to stumble upon hidden gold...
Source: http://www.nipponanimation.com/catalogue/030/index.html
See also: http://www.pelleas.net/dbman/db.cgi?db=wmt&amp;uid=default&amp;ID=011&amp;view_records=1</description>
